    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>By studying a demonic opponent, you can sense and target its weak spots.</p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl38_LabelType\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl38_LabelType\">Mendev Crusaders</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>You can attempt a Knowledge (planes) check to find a demon's weak spot. (DC 10 + the demon's CR). If you succeed, you gain a +3 trait bonus on rolls to confirm critical hits against that demon until the end of the battle. This effect only works on demons.</p>",
